headline: FMC (FMC) Tops Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: FMC (FMC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 125% and 1.59%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Corteva Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: Corteva, Inc. (NYSE: CTVA) today announced its Board of Directors has authorized a common stock dividend of $0.17 cents per share, payable June 16, 2025, to the Company's shareholders of record on June 2, 2025.
